{"tid":100994,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[城市巨人][有圖]屌你老母個死肥婆想壓死我","createTime":"2017-01-30T13:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T05:24:33.000Z","uid":6097,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6b143f5687a51a10a9c2f3f5ff09fb6643ade8e","tid":100994,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"(頭先無分台)<br />\n我屌佢老母<br />\n一出車就已經覺得啲燈光暗咗一半<br />\n唔撚緊要 肥人有肥人生活<br />\n人不犯我 我不犯人<br />\n呀屌你老母 你咁嘅身軀仲要挨咗條柱<br />\n我不停咁見到成舊坦克咁係我面前fing黎fing去 <br />\n一路諗我未撚寫遺書架 你咪撚跌落黎呀<br />\n架車真係突然chok一chok<br />\n心都嚇到跳埋出黎<br />\n好彩個不倒翁搖返去另一邊<br />\n佢其間仲要又撥頭髮 但見到佢把頭髮同個欣宜妝<br />\n只諗到呀SA嗰句:我想嘔呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCJSH33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCJSH33.jpg&h=8b7d864b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5923bba7f2362d714c84c9ac0b8c8fab3a0be58","tid":100994,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade8c4a4b1adf8f5420b30a3df94e85e49316b44","tid":100994,"uid":80508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d798cc5e0833db641cd00e5b9fa3b6ddc7c8d7ae","tid":100994,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos